examples.en: A tree was propped up by iron stays.
I hope Tim stays out of trouble this year.
He stays in good shape by lifting weights.
The family that prays together stays together.
She's a parasite who only stays with him for the money.
She stays in shape by exercising daily and eating well.
He stays home from work whenever he feels the least indisposed.
I hope it stays fine for you.
As long as the economy stays on course, the future looks rosy.
I don't know why he stays with her  she treats him like dirt.
If this fine weather stays, we shall be able to lay the wheat by next week.
The town library stays open primarily through beneficences from concerned residents.
Breakfast cereal consisting of agglomerated clusters of wheat, rice, and nuts stays crunchy in milk.
